<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-the-trouble-to-do-sth">take the trouble to do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>费神做某事；不辞辛劳地做某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My parents have given me life and take all the trouble to bring me up.
父母给了我生命并含辛茹苦地把我养大。</p><footer>2009 福建书面表达改</footer></div></div>